title: Dudley the Flying Cat
features: Let your sense of wonder take flight with this loveable children's book about an unforgettable journey with Dudley the Flying Cat.
Dudley the Flying Cat is a tale about a small boy with a big imagination, as he embarks on an adventure with a not-so-average cat named Dudley.
Narrated through the voice of a child, enjoy a story that takes readers to a place where dreams come true and creativity soars.
description: Toxey Overstreet author of Dudley the Flying Cat.
